Necessary factors:
1. Donald Trump is alive in 2023.
2. Twitter allows Donald Trump's @realdonaldtrump account access in 2023.
3. Donald Trump decides to tweet at least once on @realdonaldtrump in 2023.

1. P(Donald Trump is alive in 2023)=0.98
2. P(Twitter allows Donald Trump's @realdonaldtrump account access in 2023 | Donald Trump is alive in 2023)=0.45
3. P(Donald Trump decides to tweet at least once on @realdonaldtrump in 2023 | Twitter allows Donald Trump's @realdonaldtrump account access in 2023, Donald Trump is alive in 2023)=0.95

Multiplying out the probabilities: 0.98*0.45*0.95=0.41865
0.41865